     F*          |     |          |          EXPANSION OF THE "KANBAN"*
     F*********************************************** ABMR26 **********
     FABMWP21 UF  E                    DISK
     FGHDTL21 IF  E           K        DISK
     FADHTL05 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABMPPB5 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABMPPB6 IF  E           K        DISK
